Detailed Description

template<class T>
class Util::Linkable< T >

Base class to make cells linkable in single linked list

To be (de)linkable in single linked list, a cell must be instance of a class derived from class Linkable. A linkable cell may be in at most one queue. A linkable class must be declared as follow : 

  class X : public Linkable<X> {
  ..; members etc...
  };
